title: Episode 165: Young and Energized (Feat. Moneybagg Yo & Monyetta Shaw)
itunes:title: Episode 165: Young and Energized (Feat. Moneybagg Yo & Monyetta Shaw)
description:
Rapper Moneybagg Yo and Author Monyetta Shaw join the ladies of Lip Service this week and play the new Lip Service card game! Also, Moneybagg Yo opens up about his childhood crushes, lying to women during sex, and much more. He even hands over his phone and lets Angela go through his Instagram searches and DM's! Purchase your own Lip Service card game at www.lipservicegame.com to get in on the fun.
